<!-- Definition and symptoms -->
'''流產'''（{{lang|en|miscarriage}}），又稱'''自然流產'''（{{lang|en|spontaneous abortion}} 或 {{lang|en|pregnancy loss}}），俗稱'''小產'''。是指[[胚胎|胚胎]]或[[胎兒|胎兒]]發育到{{le|胎兒存活率|Fetal viability|可在子宮外獨立生存}}之前的自然死亡<ref name=John2012/><ref name=NIH2013Def>{{cite web|title=What is pregnancy loss/miscarriage?|url=http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/pregnancyloss/conditioninfo/Pages/default.aspx|website=www.nichd.nih.gov/|accessdate=14 March 2015|date=2013-07-15|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402121055/http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/pregnancyloss/conditioninfo/Pages/default.aspx|archivedate=2015-04-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。有些以[[孕齡|孕齡]]20週為界，之前的胎兒死亡稱為流產，之後的則稱為[[死產|死產]]<ref name=NIH2014Def>{{cite web|title=Stillbirth: Overview|url=https://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/stillbirth/Pages/default.aspx|website=NICHD|accessdate=4 October 2016|date=23 September 2014|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161005085055/https://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/stillbirth/Pages/default.aspx|archivedate=2016-10-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。流產最常見症狀是{{le|陰道出血|vaginal bleeding}}有或沒有伴隨疼痛<ref name=John2012/>。在這之後可能感到[[悲傷|悲傷]]、[[焦慮|焦慮]]、以及[[罪惡感|罪惡感]]<ref name="Pregnancy loss">{{cite journal|last1=Robinson|first1=GE|title=Pregnancy loss|journal=Best Practice & Research. Clinical Obstetrics & Gynaecology|date=January 2014|volume=28|issue=1|pages=169–78|pmid=24047642|doi=10.1016/j.bpobgyn.2013.08.012}}</ref><ref name = radford>{{Cite journal|last=Radford|first=Eleanor J|last2=Hughes|first2=Mark|date=2015-06-01|title=Women's experiences of early miscarriage: implications for nursing care|journal=Journal of Clinical Nursing|volume=24|issue=11–12|pages=1457–1465|doi=10.1111/jocn.12781|pmid=25662397|issn=1365-2702}}</ref>。[[組織_(生物學)|組織]]與[[血栓|血塊]]狀物質也可能從[[陰道|陰道]]流出<ref>{{cite web|title=What are the symptoms of pregnancy loss/miscarriage?|url=http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/pregnancyloss/conditioninfo/Pages/symptoms.aspx|website=www.nichd.nih.gov/|accessdate=14 March 2015|date=2013-07-15|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402113638/http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/pregnancyloss/conditioninfo/Pages/symptoms.aspx|archivedate=2015-04-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。當婦女一直持續發生流產時，就算是[[不孕|不孕]]症<ref name="gloss">{{Cite web|url=https://www.womenshealth.gov/glossary/|title=Glossary {{!}} womenshealth.gov|website=womenshealth.gov|access-date=2017-09-11|date=January 10, 2017|archive-date=2021-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210203014952/https://www.womenshealth.gov/glossary/|dead-url=no}}{{PD-notice}}</ref>。若只是陰道輕微出血，但胎兒繼續成長，則稱為'''[[先兆流產|先兆流產]]'''（{{lang|en|threatened abortion}}）<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.fhs.gov.hk/tc_chi/health_info/woman/15681.html |title=家庭健康服務 - 健康資訊 >> 婦女健康 |accessdate=2018-11-07 |archive-date=2020-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201022195455/https://www.fhs.gov.hk/tc_chi/health_info/woman/15681.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>或'''作小產'''<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20100331/00176_049.html |title=懷孕初期 勿早下判斷 |accessdate=2018-11-07 |archive-date=2020-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201022195500/http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20100331/00176_049.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

<!-- Risk factors and diagnosis -->
流產的危險因子包括高齡、流產史、接觸[[香菸|香菸]]、[[肥胖|肥胖]]、[[糖尿病|糖尿病]]、[[甲狀腺疾病|甲狀腺疾病]]、使用[[藥物|藥物]]、[[毒品|毒品]]或[[酒|酒精]]等等<ref name="NIH2013Epi" /><ref name="Ol2014" /> 。大約80％的流產發生在[[懷孕|懷孕]]的前12週（前三個月，又稱第一期）<ref name="John2012" /> 。大約半數的病例具有[[染色體變異|染色體變異]]<ref name="Vai2015">{{cite journal|last1=Vaiman|first1=Daniel|title=Genetic regulation of recurrent spontaneous abortion in humans|journal=Biomedical Journal|volume=38|issue=1|year=2015|pages=11–24|doi=10.4103/2319-4170.133777|pmid=25179715}}</ref><ref name="John2012" />。流產診斷可以檢查[[子宮頸|子宮頸]]的開合、血中[[人绒毛膜促性腺激素|人绒毛膜促性腺激素]]（hCG）的濃度和[[超音波|超音波]]檢查<ref name="NIH2015Diag">{{cite web|title=How do health care providers diagnose pregnancy loss or miscarriage?|url=http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/pregnancyloss/conditioninfo/Pages/diagnosed.aspx|website=www.nichd.nih.gov/|accessdate=14 March 2015|date=2013-07-15|archive-date=2017-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171222071656/https://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/pregnancyloss/conditioninfo/Pages/diagnosed.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。會產生類似症狀的其他疾病包括[[異位妊娠|異位妊娠]]和{{le|著床出血|Iimplantation bleeding}}<ref name="John2012" />。

<!-- Prevention and treatment -->
良好的[[產前護理|產前護理]]與完善的[[產前檢查|產前檢查]]可能預防流產發生<ref name="NIH2013Pre" />。避免使用藥物及酒精、預防[[感染|感染]]性疾病、避免[[輻射|輻射]]曝露可能會減少流產的風險<ref name="NIH2013Pre">{{cite web|title=Is there a cure for pregnancy loss/miscarriage?|url=http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/pregnancyloss/conditioninfo/Pages/cure.aspx|website=www.nichd.nih.gov/|accessdate=14 March 2015|date=2013-10-21|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402181042/http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/pregnancyloss/conditioninfo/Pages/cure.aspx|archivedate=2015-04-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。流產後的七至十四天通常無須特別的治療<ref name="Ol2014" /><ref name="NIH2013Tx" />。多數流產無需人為介入就會完成<ref name="Ol2014" />。有時會使用藥物[[米索前列醇|米索前列醇]]或{{tsl|en|vacuum aspiration|真空抽吸術}}協助剩餘妊娠組織的排出<ref name="NIH2013Tx" /><ref name="#1">{{cite journal|last1=Tunçalp|first1=O|last2=Gülmezoglu|first2=AM|last3=Souza|first3=JP|title=Surgical procedures for evacuating incomplete miscarriage|journal=The Cochrane Database of Systematic Reviews|date=8 September 2010|issue=9|pages=CD001993|pmid=20824830|doi=10.1002/14651858.CD001993.pub2}}</ref>。血型是[[Rh血型系统|Rh]]陰性的婦女可能需要使用{{tsl|en|Rho(D) immune globulin||Rho(D) 免疫球蛋白}}<ref name=Ol2014>{{cite journal|last1=Oliver|first1=A|last2=Overton|first2=C|title=Diagnosis and management of miscarriage|journal=The Practitioner|date=May 2014|volume=258|issue=1771|pages=25–8, 3|pmid=25055407}}</ref>。[[止痛藥|止痛藥]]可能會有益於疼痛控制<ref name=NIH2013Tx/>。情感支持也有助於負面情緒的控制<ref name=NIH2013Tx>{{cite web|title=What are the treatments for pregnancy loss/miscarriage?|url=http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/pregnancyloss/conditioninfo/Pages/treatments.aspx|website=www.nichd.nih.gov|accessdate=14 March 2015|date=2013-07-15|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402121052/http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/pregnancyloss/conditioninfo/Pages/treatments.aspx|archivedate=2015-04-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

<!-- Epidemiology -->
流產是[[妊娠|妊娠]]早期最常見的[[併發症|併發症]]<ref name="NICE-2012">{{cite web|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmedhealth/PMH0055257/|title=Ectopic Pregnancy and Miscarriage: Diagnosis and Initial Management in Early Pregnancy of Ectopic Pregnancy and Miscarriage|last=National Coordinating Centre for Women's and Children's Health (UK)|date=December 2012|website=NICE Clinical Guidelines, No. 154|publisher=Royal College of Obstetricians and Gynaecologists|accessdate=4 July 2013|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131020003707/http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmedhealth/PMH0055257/|archivedate=2013-10-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在已知自己懷孕的婦女中，流產率約為10-20%，而所有[[受孕|受孕]]後流產的比率約為30-50%<ref name="John2012">{{cite book|title=The Johns Hopkins Manual of Gynecology and Obstetrics|date=2012|publisher=Lippincott Williams & Wilkins|isbn=9781451148015|pages=438–439|edition=4|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=4Sg5sXyiBvkC&pg=PA438|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204041547/https://books.google.com/books?id=4Sg5sXyiBvkC&pg=PA438|archivedate=2020-12-04|access-date=2019-10-20|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="NIH2013Epi">{{cite web|title=How many people are affected by or at risk for pregnancy loss or miscarriage?|url=http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/pregnancyloss/conditioninfo/Pages/risk.aspx|website=www.nichd.nih.gov|accessdate=14 March 2015|date=2013-07-15|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402093633/http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/pregnancyloss/conditioninfo/Pages/risk.aspx|archivedate=2015-04-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。流產風險與孕婦年齡有關，小於35歲大約有10%，超過40歲則約有45%<ref name="John2012" />；風險在30歲左右之後開始增加<ref name="NIH2013Epi" />。約有5％的婦女有連續兩次流產的經驗<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Garrido-Gimenez|first1=C|last2=Alijotas-Reig|first2=J|title=Recurrent miscarriage: causes, evaluation and management|journal=Postgraduate Medical Journal|date=March 2015|volume=91|issue=1073|pages=151–162|pmid=25681385|doi=10.1136/postgradmedj-2014-132672}}</ref>。有些人建議與經歷流產者討論時，不要使用[[墮胎|墮胎]]一辭，以減少其痛苦<ref>{{cite book|last1=Greaves|first1=Ian|last2=Porter|first2=Keith|last3=Hodgetts|first3=Tim J.|last4=Woollard|first4=Malcolm|title=Emergency Care: A Textbook for Paramedics|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=2Z3cMX7owGwC&pg=PA506|date=2005|publisher=Elsevier Health Sciences|location=London|isbn=978-0-7020-2586-0|page=506|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204041554/https://books.google.com/books?id=2Z3cMX7owGwC&pg=PA506|archivedate=2020-12-04|access-date=2016-06-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

{{TOC limit|3}}

==孕齡==
{{胎齡及胎兒發育}}

==症狀及體徵==
流產的表現包括{{tsl|en|vaginal spotting|陰道小量出血|}}、[[腹痛|腹痛]]、[[抽搐|絞痛]]和[[羊水|羊水]]、[[血栓|血塊]]及[[組織_(生物學)|組織]]由[[陰道|陰道]]排出<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/pregnancyloss/conditioninfo/Pages/diagnosed.aspx|title=How do health care providers diagnose pregnancy loss or miscarriage?|website=www.nichd.nih.gov|access-date=2017-11-07|archive-date=2017-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171222071656/https://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/pregnancyloss/conditioninfo/Pages/diagnosed.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{sfn|Hoffman|page=176}}<ref name=":4">{{Cite journal|title= Chinese herbal medicines for threatened miscarriage; Cochrane Database of Systematic Reviews|journal = Cochrane Database of Systematic Reviews|issue = 5|pages = CD008510|last=Li|first=Lu|last2=Dou|first2=Lixia|last3=Leung|first3=Ping Chung|last4=Wang|first4=Chi Chiu|date=2012-05-16|isbn = |doi=10.1002/14651858.cd008510.pub2|pmid = 22592730}}</ref>。[[出血|出血]]可能是流產的症狀，但是許多女性在懷孕初期出血並不會流產<ref name="auto">{{Cite news|url=https://medlineplus.gov/miscarriage.html|title=Miscarriage {{!}} Miscarriage Symptoms {{!}} MedlinePlus|access-date=2017-09-09|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170728020027/https://medlineplus.gov/miscarriage.html|archivedate=2017-07-28|dead-url=no}}{{PD-notice}}</ref>。懷孕期間出血稱為先兆流產。在懷孕期間因出血，尋求治療的人中，約有一半會流產<ref name="bmj1997">{{cite journal | author = Everett C | title = Incidence and outcome of bleeding before the 20th week of pregnancy: Prospective study from general practice | journal = BMJ | volume = 315 | issue = 7099 | pages = 32–4 | year = 1997 | pmid = 9233324 | pmc = 2127042 | doi = 10.1136/bmj.315.7099.32 }}</ref>。超音波檢查，或連續測量[[人絨毛膜促性腺激素|人絨毛膜促性腺激素]]（hCG）可能可以診斷流產。

==風險因子==
{{See|流產風險}}

流產可能源自多種原因，且並非所有原因都能找到。增加流產可能性的因素稱為[[风险因子|風險因子]]，但它們並不一定必然導致流產。多達70種情況<ref name="John2012" /><ref name="Vai2015" />{{sfn|Hoffman|page=181–182}}<ref name="auto7">{{Cite journal|last=Ali|first=Osman|last2=Hakimi|first2=Ihssane|last3=Chanana|first3=Adil|last4=Habib|first4=My Abdellah Baba|last5=Guelzim|first5=Khalid|last6=Kouach|first6=Jaouad|last7=Rahali|first7=Driss Moussaoui|last8=Dehayeni|first8=Mohammed|date=2015|title=[Term pegnancy on septate uterus: report of a case and review of the literature]|journal=The Pan African Medical Journal|volume=22|pages=219|doi=10.11604/pamj.2015.22.219.7790|issn=1937-8688| pmc=4760728 |pmid=26955410}}</ref><ref name="TersigniCastellani2014">{{cite journal|last1=Tersigni|first1=C.|last2=Castellani|first2=R.|last3=de Waure|first3=C.|last4=Fattorossi|first4=A.|last5=De Spirito|first5=M.|last6=Gasbarrini|first6=A.|last7=Scambia|first7=G.|last8=Di Simone|first8=N.|year=2014|title=Celiac disease and reproductive disorders: meta-analysis of epidemiologic associations and potential pathogenic mechanisms|journal=Human Reproduction Update|volume=20|issue=4|pages=582–593|doi=10.1093/humupd/dmu007|issn=1355-4786|pmid=24619876}}</ref>{{sfn|Hoffman|page = 172}}、感染<ref name="auto1">{{cite web|url=http://www.nhs.uk/Conditions/Miscarriage/Pages/Causes.aspx|title=Miscarriage - Causes - NHS Choices|first=NHS|last=Choices|website=www.nhs.uk|date=December 7, 2017|accessdate=2019-10-20|archive-date=2017-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170927183537/http://www.nhs.uk/Conditions/Miscarriage/Pages/causes.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="American College of Obstetricians and 372–9">{{cite journal|last=American College of Obstetricians and|first=Gynecologists|title=ACOG Practice Bulletin No.142: Cerclage for the management of cervical insufficiency|journal=Obstetrics and Gynecology|date=Feb 2014|volume=123|issue=2 Pt 1|pages=372–9|pmid=24451674|doi=10.1097/01.AOG.0000443276.68274.cc}}</ref><ref name="LisRowhani-Rahbar2015">{{cite journal|last1=Lis|first1=R.|last2=Rowhani-Rahbar|first2=A.|last3=Manhart|first3=L. E.|title=Mycoplasma genitalium Infection and Female Reproductive Tract Disease: A Meta-Analysis|journal=Clinical Infectious Diseases|year=2015|issn=1058-4838|doi=10.1093/cid/civ312|pmid=25900174|volume=61|issue=3|pages=418–26}}</ref>、醫療處置<ref name="Agarwal-Alfirevic-2012">{{cite journal|date=August 2012|title=Pregnancy loss after chorionic villus sampling and genetic amniocentesis in twin pregnancies: a systematic review|journal=Ultrasound in Obstetrics & Gynecology|volume=40|issue=2|pages=128–34|doi=10.1002/uog.10152|pmid=22125091|vauthors=Agarwal K, Alfirevic Z}}</ref><ref name="Alfirevic">{{Cite book|title=Cochrane Database of Systematic Reviews|volume=9|pages=CD003252|last=Alfirevic|first=Zarko|last2=Navaratnam|first2=Kate|last3=Mujezinovic|first3=Faris|date=2017-09-04|publisher=John Wiley & Sons, Ltd|doi=10.1002/14651858.cd003252.pub2|pmid=28869276|pmc=6483702}}</ref>、生活方式<ref name="NIH2013Epi" /><ref name="Ol2014" /><ref name="x">{{cite journal |vauthors=Ness RB, Grisso JA, Hirschinger N, Markovic N, Shaw LM, Day NL, Kline J | title = Cocaine and Tobacco Use and the Risk of Spontaneous Abortion | journal = New England Journal of Medicine | volume = 340 | issue = 5 | pages = 333–9 | year = 1999 | pmid = 9929522 | doi = 10.1056/NEJM199902043400501 }}</ref><ref name="auto1"/><ref name="paternal smoking">{{cite journal |vauthors=Venners SA, Wang X, Chen C, Wang L, Chen D, Guang W, Huang A, Ryan L, O'Connor J, Lasley B, Overstreet J, Wilcox A, Xu X | title = Paternal Smoking and Pregnancy Loss: A Prospective Study Using a Biomarker of Pregnancy | journal = American Journal of Epidemiology | volume = 159 | issue = 10 | pages = 993–1001 | year = 2004 | pmid = 15128612 | doi = 10.1093/aje/kwh128 }}</ref>、職業暴露<ref name="NIH2013Pre" />{{sfn|Hoffman|page=173}}{{sfn|Hoffman|page=272}}、化學暴露{{sfn|Hoffman|page=272}}和輪班工作與流產風險增加有關<ref name="chav">{{cite journal|last1=Chavarro|first1=Jorge E.|last2=Rich-Edwards|first2=Janet W.|last3=Gaskins|first3=Audrey J.|last4=Farland|first4=Leslie V.|last5=Terry|first5=Kathryn L.|last6=Zhang|first6=Cuilin|last7=Missmer|first7=Stacey A.|title=Contributions of the Nurses' Health Studies to Reproductive Health Research|journal=American Journal of Public Health|volume=106|issue=9|year=2016|pages=1669–1676|issn=0090-0036|doi=10.2105/AJPH.2016.303350|pmid=27459445|pmc=4981818}}(review)</ref>。其它風險因子還包括[[內分泌系統|內分泌系統]]、[[遺傳學|遺傳學]]、[[子宮|子宮]]構造或[[激素|激素]]的異常、生殖道感染和[[自體免疫性疾病|自體免疫性疾病]]引起的[[移植排斥|組織排斥反應]]<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Acién|first=Pedro|last2=Acién|first2=Maribel|date=2016-01-01|title=The presentation and management of complex female genital malformations|journal=Human Reproduction Update|volume=22|issue=1|pages=48–69|doi=10.1093/humupd/dmv048|pmid=26537987|issn=1355-4786}}</ref>。

=== 孕期 ===
==== 第一孕期 ====
{| class="wikitable" style = "float: right; margin-left:15px; text-align:center"
|+懷孕第一期流產時發現的染色體異常
!說明
!佔總數比率
|-
|[[XY性別決定系統|正常]]
|45–55％
|-
|[[染色體三倍體症|染色體三倍體症]]
|22–32％
|-
|[[特納氏綜合征|X 染色體單體 (45, X)]]
|5–20％
|-
|{{tsl|en|Triploid syndrome|三倍體}} 
|6–8％
|-
|染色體[[染色體畸變|結構異常]]
|2％
|-
|雙重的或三重的三染色體
|0.7-2.0％{{sfn|Hoffman|page=171}}
|-
|[[染色體易位|染色體易位]]
|不明<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.acog.org/-/media/For-Patients/faq100.pdf?dmc=1&ts=20150820T1255284207 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2019-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170914125252/https://www.acog.org/-/media/For-Patients/faq100.pdf?dmc=1&ts=20150820T1255284207 |archive-date=2017-09-14 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>
|}

多數臨床上明顯的流產（在各種研究中占了三分之二至四分之三）發生在第一孕期，也就是懷孕的前三個月<ref name="John2012" /><ref name="auto1"/><ref name="webmd">{{cite web | last = Rosenthal | first = M. Sara | title = The Second Trimester | website = The Gynecological Sourcebook | publisher = WebMD | year = 1999 | url = http://www.webmd.com/content/article/4/1680_51802.htm | accessdate = December 18, 2006 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20061201085538/http://www.webmd.com/content/article/4/1680_51802.htm | archivedate = 2006-12-01 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name=Will2013>{{Cite book|title=Williams Obstetrics|last=Cunningham|first=F, Leveno KJ, Bloom SL, Spong CY, Dashe JS, Hoffman BL, Casey BM, Sheffield JS|publisher=McGraw-Hill|year=2013|isbn=|location=|pages=5|chapter=Abortion}}</ref>。所有受精卵中約有30-40％會流產，通常在還不知道懷孕前就發生了<ref name=John2012/>。一般胚胎在被排出前就已死亡；出血至底蛻膜（{{lang|en|decidua basalis}}）內和組織壞死會引起子宮收縮，將妊娠組織排出<ref name=Will2013 />。早期流產可能是因為胎盤或其他胚胎組織的發育異常。在某些情況下，不會形成胚胎，且仍其它組織形成。被稱為'''萎縮性胚囊'''或'''萎縮卵'''（{{lang|en|blighted ovum}}）<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://americanpregnancy.org/pregnancy-complications/blighted-ovum/|title=Blighted Ovum: Symptoms, Causes and Prevention|date=2012-04-26|work=American Pregnancy Association|access-date=2017-09-09|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170725113127/http://americanpregnancy.org/pregnancy-complications/blighted-ovum/|archivedate=2017-07-25|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.mayoclinic.org/diseases-conditions/pregnancy-loss-miscarriage/expert-answers/blighted-ovum/faq-20057783|title=Blighted ovum: What causes it?|work=Mayo Clinic|access-date=2017-09-09|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170720141145/http://www.mayoclinic.org/diseases-conditions/pregnancy-loss-miscarriage/expert-answers/blighted-ovum/faq-20057783|archivedate=2017-07-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{sfn|Hoffman|page=171}}，在台灣俗稱「空包蛋」或「空包彈」。

[[受精卵|受精卵]]最可能在受孕後第8-10天成功在[[子宮|子宮]]內[[着床|著床]]。如果受精卵在第10天仍未著床，成功著床的機率將隨時間增加到遞減<ref name="pmid10362823">{{cite journal|title=Time of implantation of the conceptus and loss of pregnancy|journal=[[新英格蘭醫學雜志|The New England Journal of Medicine]]|issue=23|doi=10.1056/NEJM199906103402304|year=1999|volume=340|pages=1796–1799|pmid=10362823|vauthors=Wilcox AJ, Baird DD, Weinberg CR}}</ref>。

化學妊娠是指檢驗陽性而發現的懷孕，但在下一個預期生理週期之前或前後因流產而告終<ref>{{cite book|last1=Condous|first1=edited by Tom Bourne, George|title=Handbook of early pregnancy care|date=2006|publisher=Informa Healthcare|location=London|isbn=9780203016213|pages=28–29|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=_Y3PyNvc6dcC&pg=PA29|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204041607/https://books.google.com/books?id=_Y3PyNvc6dcC&pg=PA29|archivedate=2020-12-04|access-date=2019-10-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在懷孕前13週內流產的胚胎，超過一半具有染色體異常。半數的胚胎流產（佔所有流產的25％）具有[[非整倍體|非整倍體]]（染色體數目異常）<ref>{{cite journal|title=Anatomic and chromosomal anomalies in 639 spontaneous abortuses|journal=Human Genetics|issue=1|doi=10.1007/BF00329132|year=1980|volume=55|pages=87–98|pmid=7450760|vauthors=Kajii T, Ferrier A, Niikawa N, Takahara H, Ohama K, Avirachan S}}</ref>。流產中常見的染色體異常包括[[染色體三倍體症|染色體三倍體症]]（22–32%）、[[特纳氏综合征|X 染色體單體]]（5–20%）、{{tsl|en|Triploid syndrome|三倍體}}（6–8%）、[[同源多倍體|同源多倍體]]（2–4%）或其他染色體結構異常（2％）。年齡較大的父母更容易發生基因的問題；這可能是在年長婦女流產率較高的原因<ref>{{cite web|title=Pregnancy Over Age 30|url=http://www.musckids.com/health_library/hrpregnant/over30.htm|accessdate=December 18, 2006|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20061113233603/http://www.musckids.com/health_library/hrpregnant/over30.htm|archivedate=2006-11-13|website=MUSC Children's Hospital|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

沒有證據支援在第一孕期使用黃體酮可以降低流產風險，而黃體期孕酮缺乏不一定是造成流產的因素<ref name="Cochrane">{{cite journal|title=Progestogen for treating threatened miscarriage|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmedhealth/PMH0013622/|journal=Cochrane Database of Systematic Reviews|issue=12|doi=10.1002/14651858.CD005943.pub4|year=2011|pages=CD005943|pmid=22161393|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131020003112/http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmedhealth/PMH0013622/|archivedate=2013-10-20|vauthors=Wahabi HA, Fayed AA, Esmaeil SA, Al Zeidan RA|editor1-last=Wahabi|editor1-first=Hayfaa A|access-date=2019-10-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{Update inline|reason=Updated version https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/30081430|date=November 2018}}<ref>{{cite journal|title=Luteal phase defect: Myth or reality|journal=Obstetrics and Gynecology Clinics of North America|issue=4|doi=10.1016/j.ogc.2004.08.007|year=2004|volume=31|pages=727–44, ix|pmid=15550332|vauthors=Bukulmez O, Arici A}}</ref>。

==== 第二孕期和第三孕期 ====
第二孕期流產可能由母親因素造成，如：[[子宫畸形|子宮畸形]]、子宮內的發育（[[子宮肌瘤|肌瘤]]）或[[宫颈机能不全|子宮頸的問題]]。這些狀況也可能導致[[早產|早產]]。與第一孕期流產不同，第二孕期流產較少由遺傳基因異常；在三分之一的病例中發現染色體畸變。第三孕期感染會造成流產。

=== 年齡 ===
<!--- {{Further|Advanced maternal age}} 高齡產婦--->
孕婦的年齡是重要的危險因素。流產率隨著年齡增長而持續增加；35歲後，流產率更是大幅上升<ref>{{cite journal|author=Bray I, Gunnell D, Davey Smith G|year=2006|title=Advanced paternal age: How old is too old?|journal=Journal of Epidemiology & Community Health|volume=60|issue=10|pages=851–3|doi=10.1136/jech.2005.045179|pmc=2566050|pmid=16973530}}</ref>。35歲以下的，流產風險約為10％；但40歲以上者，風險約為45％<ref name="John2012" />。在30歲左右，風險就會開始增加<ref name="NIH2013Epi" />。{{tsl|en|Paternal age effect|父親年齡}}增加也與流產風險增加有關{{sfn|Hoffman|page=175}}。

=== 肥胖、飲食失調和咖啡因 ===
肥胖不僅與流產有關；也可能導致不孕和其他懷孕相關的併發症。[[反覆流產|反覆流產]]也和肥胖有關。患有[[神經性暴食症|神經性暴食症]]與[[神經性厭食症|神經性厭食症]]的女性的流產風險可能更高。尚未發現營養缺乏會影響流產率，但[[妊娠劇吐|妊娠劇吐]]有時會在流產前發生{{sfn|Hoffman|page=173}}。

[[咖啡因|咖啡因]]的攝取量與流產率成正比，至少在攝取量較高時是這樣的<ref name="auto1"/>。然而，這樣較高的比率僅在某些情況才有統計顯著差異。

補充[[維生素|維生素]]通常無法有效預防流產<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Cochrane Database of Systematic Reviews|journal = Cochrane Database of Systematic Reviews|issue = 5|pages = CD004073|last=Balogun|first=Olukunmi O|last2=da Silva Lopes|first2=Katharina|last3=Ota|first3=Erika|last4=Takemoto|first4=Yo|last5=Rumbold|first5=Alice|last6=Takegata|first6=Mizuki|last7=Mori|first7=Rintaro|date=2016-05-06|isbn = |doi=10.1002/14651858.cd004073.pub4|pmid = 27150280}}</ref>。也未發現可以預防流產的傳統中藥治療<ref name=":4" />。

=== 內分泌失調 ===
[[甲狀腺疾病|甲狀腺疾病]]可能會影響妊娠結果。與此有關，[[碘缺乏病|碘缺乏]]與流產風險增加的關係密切{{sfn|Hoffman|page=173}}。[[胰岛素依赖型糖尿病|胰島素依賴型糖尿病]]患者，血糖控制不佳與流產風險增加有關{{sfn|Hoffman|page=173}}。糖尿病控制良好的婦女與沒有糖尿病的婦女，兩者的流產風險相同<ref name="Ferri2017">{{cite book|author=Fred F. Ferri|title=Ferri's Clinical Advisor 2017|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=rRhCDAAAQBAJ&pg=PA1198|year=2017|publisher=Elsevier|isbn=978-0-323-28048-8|page=1198|access-date=2019-10-21|archive-date=2020-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204041629/https://books.google.com/books?id=rRhCDAAAQBAJ&pg=PA1198|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="MehtaGupta2018">{{cite book|author1=Sumita Mehta|author2=Bindiya Gupta|title=Recurrent Pregnancy Loss|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=5KZWDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA185|year=2018|publisher=Springer|isbn=978-981-10-7337-3|page=185|access-date=2019-10-21|archive-date=2020-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204041648/https://books.google.com/books?id=5KZWDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA185|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 食物中毒 ===
食用被{{tsl|en|listeriosis|李斯特菌|}}、[[弓形蟲|弓形蟲]]（[[弓蟲症|弓蟲症]]）和[[沙門氏菌屬|沙門氏菌]]污染的食物會增加流產的風險<ref name="auto1" /><ref name="gloss" />。

=== 羊膜穿刺術和絨毛取樣術 ===
[[羊膜穿刺術|羊膜穿刺術]]和[[絨毛取樣術|絨毛取樣術]]（CVS）是檢查胎兒的方法。將細針穿過腹部，進入子宮取得羊水樣本。絨毛膜絨毛取樣過程類似，但取樣的對象是組織而非羊水。在妊娠第二期進行這些程序與流產無關，但在第一孕期進行則與流產和胎兒出生缺陷有關<ref name="Alfirevic"/>。侵入性產前診斷檢查（絨毛取樣術和羊膜穿刺術）很少引起流產（約1％）<ref name="Agarwal-Alfirevic-2012"/>。

=== 手術 ===
手術（包括[[減肥手術|減肥手術]]）對懷孕的影響仍不完全清楚。腹部和骨盆手術不是流產的危險因子。切除的卵巢腫瘤和囊腫並不會增加流產風險。但若將卵巢中的[[黃體|黃體]]移除，可能會導致維持妊娠所需的激素變化，進而增加流產的風險{{sfn|Hoffman|pages=172–173}}。

=== 藥物 ===
曾使用[[抗抑鬱藥|抗抑鬱藥]]與自然流產間沒有顯著關聯<ref name="Ross LE 436–443">{{Cite journal|last=Ross LE|last2=Grigoriadis S|last3=Mamisashvili L|display-authors=etal|date=2013-04-01|title=Selected pregnancy and delivery outcomes after exposure to antidepressant medication: A systematic review and meta-analysis|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_jama-psychiatry_2013-04_70_4/page/436|journal=JAMA Psychiatry|volume=70|issue=4|pages=436–443|doi=10.1001/jamapsychiatry.2013.684|pmid=23446732|issn=2168-622X}}</ref>。在懷孕前預防性停用 [[SSRIs|SSRIs]] 並未明顯降低流產的風險<ref name="auto3">{{Cite journal|last=Dalke|first=Katharine Baratz|last2=Wenzel|first2=Amy|last3=Kim|first3=Deborah R.|date=2016-04-19|title=Depression and Anxiety During Pregnancy: Evaluating the Literature in Support of Clinical Risk-Benefit Decision-Making|journal=Current Psychiatry Reports|volume=18|issue=6|pages=59|doi=10.1007/s11920-016-0698-x|pmid=27091646|issn=1523-3812}}</ref>。一些現有數據顯示服用任何一種[[抗抑鬱藥|抗抑鬱藥]]的婦女，會些微增加流產的風險<ref name="auto4">{{cite journal|year=2010|title=Gestational exposure to antidepressants and the risk of spontaneous abortion: A review|journal=Current Drug Delivery|volume=7|issue=1|pages=76–92|doi=10.2174/156720110790396508|pmid=19863482|vauthors=Broy P, Bérard A}}</ref><ref name="auto5">{{cite journal|year=2010|title=Use of antidepressants during pregnancy and the risk of spontaneous abortion|journal=Canadian Medical Association Journal|volume=182|issue=10|pages=1031–7|doi=10.1503/cmaj.091208|pmc=2900326|pmid=20513781|vauthors=Nakhai-Pour HR, Broy P, Bérard A}}</ref>，然而在排除那些研究品質較差的研究後，流產風險在統計的[[顯著性差異|差異顯著性]]也跟著下降<ref name="Ross LE 436–443"/><ref name="auto6">{{Cite journal|last=Yonkers|first=Kimberly A.|last2=Blackwell|first2=Katherine A.|last3=Glover|first3=Janis|last4=Forray|first4=Ariadna|date=2014-01-01|title=Antidepressant Use in Pregnant and Postpartum Women|journal=Annual Review of Clinical Psychology|volume=10|issue=1|pages=369–392|doi=10.1146/annurev-clinpsy-032813-153626|pmc=4138492|pmid=24313569}}</ref>。

會增加流產風險的藥物包括：
*{{tsl|en|retinoids|類維生素A}}（retinoids）
*[[非類固醇消炎止痛藥|非類固醇消炎止痛藥]]（NSAIDs），如：[[布洛芬|布洛芬]]（ibuprofen）
*[[米索前列醇|米索前列醇]]（misoprostol）
*[[氨甲蝶呤|氨甲蝶呤]]（methotrexate，MTX）<ref name="auto1"/>
*[[他汀類藥物|他汀類藥物]]（statin）<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Grundy|first=Scott M.|last2=Stone|first2=Neil J.|last3=Bailey|first3=Alison L.|last4=Beam|first4=Craig|last5=Birtcher|first5=Kim K.|last6=Blumenthal|first6=Roger S.|last7=Braun|first7=Lynne T.|last8=de Ferranti|first8=Sarah|last9=Faiella-Tommasino|first9=Joseph|date=2019|title=2018 AHA/ACC/AACVPR/AAPA/ABC/ACPM/ADA/AGS/APhA/ASPC/NLA/PCNA Guideline on the Management of Blood Cholesterol: Executive Summary|url=https://doi.org/10.1016/j.jacc.2018.11.002|journal=Journal of the American College of Cardiology|volume=73|issue=24|pages=3168–3209|doi=10.1016/j.jacc.2018.11.002|issn=0735-1097|via=}}</ref>

=== 疫苗接種 ===
尚未發現[[疫苗接種|疫苗接種]]會引起流產{{sfn|Hoffman|page=72}}。活性[[疫苗|疫苗]]（如：[[MMR混合疫苗|MMR]]）是可以穿過胎盤的活病毒，因此，理論上可以造成胎兒感染，並因此可能增加流產風險<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Mor|first=Gil|last2=Racicot|first2=Karen|date=2017-05-01|title=Risks associated with viral infections during pregnancy|url=https://www.jci.org/articles/view/87490|journal=The Journal of Clinical Investigation|volume=127|issue=5|pages=1591–1599|doi=10.1172/JCI87490|issn=0021-9738|access-date=2019-10-23|archive-date=2020-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204041723/https://www.jci.org/articles/view/87490|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":6">{{Cite journal|last=Bozzo|first=Pina|last2=Narducci|first2=Andrea|last3=Einarson|first3=Adrienne|date=2011|title=Vaccination during pregnancy|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3093587/|journal=Canadian Family Physician|volume=57|issue=5|pages=555–557|issn=0008-350X|pmc=3093587|pmid=21571717|via=|access-date=2019-10-23|archive-date=2020-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204041659/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3093587/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。因此，[[美國疾病控制與預防中心|美國疾病控制與預防中心]]（CDC）建議孕婦不要施打活性疫苗<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cdc.gov/vaccines/pregnancy/hcp-toolkit/guidelines.html|title=Pregnancy Guidelines and Recommendations by Vaccine {{!}} CDC|date=2019-04-19|website=www.cdc.gov|access-date=2019-08-01|archive-date=2020-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200406003822/https://www.cdc.gov/vaccines/pregnancy/hcp-toolkit/guidelines.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。但是，目前仍無明確證據顯示接種活性疫苗會增加流產或胎兒異常的風險<ref name=":6" />。

一些活性疫苗包括：[[麻疹腮腺炎德國麻疹混合疫苗|麻疹腮腺炎德國麻疹混合疫苗]]、[[水痘疫苗|水痘疫苗]]、某些類型的[[季節性流感疫苗|季節性流感疫苗]]及[[輪狀病毒疫苗|輪狀病毒疫苗]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cdc.gov/vaccines/vpd/vaccines-list.html|title=List of Vaccines {{!}} CDC|date=2019-04-15|website=www.cdc.gov|language=en-us|access-date=2019-08-06|archive-date=2019-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191030185506/https://www.cdc.gov/vaccines/vpd/vaccines-list.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.vaccines.gov/basics/types|title=Vaccine Types {{!}} Vaccines|website=www.vaccines.gov|access-date=2019-08-06|archive-date=2019-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190523191043/https://www.vaccines.gov/basics/types|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 癌症治療 ===
癌症治療期間，女性因接受[[放射線療法|放射線療法]]而暴露的[[遊離輻射|遊離輻射]]總量會導致流產，也會影響[[生育力|生育力]]。以[[化學療法|化學療法]]治療{{tsl|en|childhood cancer|兒童癌症}}也會增加流產的風險{{sfn|Hoffman|page=173}}。

=== 並發疾病 ===
數種{{tsl|en|intercurrent diseases in pregnancy|懷孕時的並發疾病|}}可能會增加流產風險，包括：[[糖尿病|糖尿病]]、[[多囊卵巢症候群|多囊卵巢症候群]]（PCOS）、[[甲狀腺機能低下症|甲狀腺機能低下症]]、某些[[傳染病|傳染病]]和[[自體免疫疾病|自體免疫疾病]]。PCOS 可能會增加流產風險<ref name="auto1"/>。兩個研究建議[[二甲双胍|二甲雙胍]]（metformin）治療可顯著降低 PCOS 婦女的流產率<ref>{{cite journal |vauthors=Jakubowicz DJ, Iuorno MJ, Jakubowicz S, Roberts KA, Nestler JE | title = Effects of Metformin on Early Pregnancy Loss in the Polycystic Ovary Syndrome | journal = Journal of Clinical Endocrinology & Metabolism | volume = 87 | issue = 2 | pages = 524–9 | year = 2002 | pmid = 11836280 | doi = 10.1210/jc.87.2.524 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |vauthors=Khattab S, Mohsen IA, Foutouh IA, Ramadan A, Moaz M, Al-Inany H | title = Metformin reduces abortion in pregnant women with polycystic ovary syndrome | journal = Gynecological Endocrinology | volume = 22 | issue = 12 | pages = 680–4 | year = 2006 | pmid = 17162710 | doi = 10.1080/09513590601010508 }}</ref>，但這些研究的品質存疑<ref name="RCOG-PCOS">{{cite web|last=Royal College of Obstetricians and Gynaecologists|title=Long-term consequences of polycystic ovarian syndrome|url=http://www.rcog.org.uk/files/rcog-corp/uploaded-files/GT33_LongTermPCOS.pdf|archive-url=https://www.webarchive.org.uk/wayback/archive/20100710113119/http://www.rcog.org.uk/files/rcog-corp/uploaded-files/GT33_LongTermPCOS.pdf|archive-date=2010-07-10|website=Green-top Guideline No. 27|publisher=Royal College of Obstetricians and Gynaecologists|accessdate=2 July 2013|date=December 2007|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。懷孕中使用二甲雙胍，尚未被確實其安全性<ref>{{cite journal |vauthors=Lilja AE, Mathiesen ER | title = Polycystic ovary syndrome and metformin in pregnancy | journal = Acta Obstetricia et Gynecologica Scandinavica | volume = 85 | issue = 7 | pages = 861–8 | year = 2006 | pmid = 16817087 | doi = 10.1080/00016340600780441 }}</ref>。2007年英國皇家婦產科學院建議不要使用這個藥物來預防流產<ref name="RCOG-PCOS" />。{{tsl|en|thrombophilia|易栓症}}（thrombophilia）或凝血和出血異常曾被認為是流產的風險因子之一，但隨後受到質疑，目前仍未有定論{{sfn|Hoffman|page=174}}。嚴重的[[甲狀腺機能低下症|甲狀腺機能低下症]]會增加流產風險，但較輕的甲狀腺功能低下對流產率的影響則尚無定論。一種名為黃體期缺損（luteal phase defect，LPD）的情況是指子宮內膜無法為懷孕做好充分準備，因而使受精卵無法正常著床，並導致流產<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.womenshealth.gov/pregnancy/you-get-pregnant/trying-conceive/#4|title=Trying to conceive {{!}} womenshealth.gov|website=womenshealth.gov|access-date=2017-09-11|date=December 13, 2016|archive-date=2021-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129093705/https://www.womenshealth.gov/pregnancy/you-get-pregnant/trying-conceive#4|dead-url=no}}{{PD-notice}}</ref>。

{{tsl|en|Mycoplasma genitalium|生殖道黴漿菌}}（''[[Mycoplasma|Mycoplasma]] genitalium''）感染與[[早產|早產]]和流產的風險增加有關<ref name="LisRowhani-Rahbar2015" />。

感染會增加流產的風險：[[風疹|風疹]]（[[德國麻疹|德國麻疹]]）、[[巨細胞病毒|巨細胞病毒]]、[[細菌性陰道病|細菌性陰道病]]、[[HIV|HIV]]、[[衣原體門|衣原體]]（[[披衣菌感染|披衣菌感染]]）、[[淋病|淋病]]、[[梅毒|梅毒]]和[[瘧疾|瘧疾]]<ref name="auto1" />。

=== 免疫狀態 ===
自體免疫可能是反覆或晚期流產的原因。在自體免疫引發的流產，媽媽的免疫系統會攻擊成長中胎兒或中終正常的懷孕進程<ref name="CarpSelmi2012">{{cite journal|year=2012|title=The autoimmune bases of infertility and pregnancy loss|journal=J Autoimmun|type=Review|volume=38|issue=2–3|pages=J266–74|doi=10.1016/j.jaut.2011.11.016|pmid=22284905|vauthors=Carp HJ, Selmi C, Shoenfeld Y}}</ref><ref name=":3">{{cite journal|year=2007|title=Female infertility due to abnormal autoimmunity: Frequently overlooked and greatly underappreciated. Part II|journal=Expert Review of Obstetrics & Gynecology|volume=2|issue=4|pages=465–75|doi=10.1586/17474108.2.4.465|vauthors=Gleicher N, Weghofer A, Barad D}}</ref>。[[自體免疫疾病|自體免疫疾病]]可能造成胚胎基因異常，進而導致流產<ref>{{cite journal|year=2011|title=Do chromosomally abnormal pregnancies really preclude autoimmune etiologies of spontaneous miscarriages?|journal=Autoimmunity Reviews|volume=10|issue=6|pages=361–3|doi=10.1016/j.autrev.2010.12.004|pmid=21195806|vauthors=Gleicher N, Weghofer A, Barad DH}}</ref>。例如，[[乳糜瀉|乳糜瀉]]會增加流產風險（{{link-en|勝算比|odds ratio}}）約 1.4 倍<ref name="TersigniCastellani2014"/>{{sfn|Hoffman|page = 172}}。免疫功能失調可能導致[[抗磷脂症候群|抗磷脂症候群]]，它會影響持續妊娠的能力，造成婦女發生[[反覆流產|反覆流產]]{{sfn|Hoffman|page=272}}。約有 15％ 的[[反覆流產|反覆流產]]與免疫有關{{sfn|Hoffman|page=182}}。患者若有[[抗甲狀腺自體抗體|抗甲狀腺自體抗體]]，[[流產|流產]]風險（{{link-en|勝算比|odds ratio}}）會增加 3.73 倍，95% [[信賴區間|信賴區間]] 1.8–7.6<ref>{{cite journal|year=2011|title=Significance of (sub)clinical thyroid dysfunction and thyroid autoimmunity before conception and in early pregnancy: A systematic review|journal=Human Reproduction Update|volume=17|issue=5|pages=605–19|doi=10.1093/humupd/dmr024|pmid=21622978|vauthors=van den Boogaard E, Vissenberg R, Land JA, van Wely M, van der Post JA, Goddijn M, Bisschop PH}}</ref>。患有[[紅斑狼瘡|紅斑狼瘡]]也會增加流產風險<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.womenshealth.gov/lupus/pregnancy-and-lupus|title=Pregnancy and lupus|website=womenshealth.gov|access-date=2017-09-11|date=April 20, 2017|archive-date=2020-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204044244/https://www.womenshealth.gov/lupus/pregnancy-and-lupus|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 結構缺陷和創傷 ===
經歷過三次或更多次反覆流產的婦女中 15％ 有的解剖學上的結構缺陷，這些結構缺陷會使妊娠期無法完全進行到順利生產{{sfn|Hoffman|page=181}}。[[子宮|子宮]]結構會影響胎兒能否孕育到足月。解剖學上的結構變異很常見，且可能是先天{{Citation needed|date=May 2019}}。
{| class="wikitable"
!子宮結構的類型
!流產率
!參考文獻
|-
|[[雙角子宮|雙角子宮]]
|40–79%
|{{sfn|Hoffman|page=181–182}}<ref name="auto7"/>
|-
|[[子宮縱隔|子宮縱隔]]或[[單角子宮|單角子宮]]
|34–88%
|{{sfn|Hoffman|page=181–182}}<ref name="auto1"/>
|-
|[[弓形子宮|弓形子宮]]
|未知
|{{sfn|Hoffman|page=181–182}}<ref name="auto1"/>
|-
|[[雙子宮畸形|雙子宮畸形]]
|40%
|{{sfn|Hoffman|page=181–182}}<ref name="auto1"/>
|-
|[[子宮肌瘤|子宮肌瘤]]
|未知
|<ref name="auto1"/>
